<p>Spacey, who made the comments in an interview for the Bits &amp; Pretzels podcast, said: 'I don't think it will come as a surprise for anyone to say that my world completely changed in the fall of 2017.</p>

<p>'My job, many of my relationships, my standing in my own industry were all gone in just a matter of hours.' </p>

<p>Not only did he get fired from Netflix hit House Of Cards, he was also removed from the completed movie All The Money In The World, which was reshot with actor Christopher Plummer in his role.</p>

